        "matcher": "Read|read|readFile|readDirectory|read_file|read_directory|FsReadFile|FsReadDirectory|fs\\.read|fs\\.readFile|fs\\.readDirectory|fs/read|fs/readFile|fs/readDirectory|fs\\\\read|fs\\\\readFile|fs\\\\readDirectory|functions\\.read|functions\\.read_file|functions\\.readFile|mcp__.*__read|mcp__.*__read_file|mcp__.*__readFile|functions\\.exec_command|exec_command|command_execution|multi_tool_use\\.parallel|Bash|Shell",
